<br>
This is a community of more mature players who tend to help each other.  The one character per account does not afford us much space to bank our items so we sell them cheeper or tend to give them away.  Please hold your reservations of others if you see them with something you know they could not obtain on their own.  People here reward lower characters for quests or help in different ways.<br>
<br>
We do have some Pling.  I am guilty of this but only in the respect that I am Pling a slave druid to carry my gear and port my party to destinations.  For the most part though it is nothing like what your used to and rare at best.<br>
<br>
This server is exactly what you are looking for if I read your post right.  It is a haven away from the choas of Pling and Twinking abroad the other servers.<br>
<br>
Join us.  RP.  Have fun.  Most of us here are<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
